Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下堂是美术课，快点到教室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 额头流血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去保健室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌的妹妹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个粗心的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理员的改造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么目的潜入美里家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊，原来是SLALLY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫的这么亲密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真难相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？她现在怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没抓到什么小辫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我可不象麻幌跟阿优那么容易相信人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要发现什么怪举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.07,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前头，对我来说你还是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会相信你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候再对我爪牙相向吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真难相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一时不注意就飞过头到台北去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能吃梅干便当啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样到傍晚就会没力气的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一今天放学后\N跟美里同学展开超级大战的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体赢不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师～老师～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.01,0:12:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看样子又想来我们家打牙祭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿石头丢她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的卤萝卜真好吃啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…就爱给人添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小笼包从天而降！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是神明的赏赐不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管家的赏赐啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，找到了，美奈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老师…还有史莱修？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…幌！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊—真危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼—吓死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和为什么老是在道歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.74,0:13:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我老是挨骂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…不用跟我道歉也可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呦，怎么了，阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险！是软弱无力滚地球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒！美奈和，有气魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么看…都觉得只是刚好跌到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉啦，那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多男孩子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家凑在一起到底要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优，赶快回攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边线出现空档了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了，阿优！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浜口，你在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在干吗，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.71,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式条老师被照明灯压到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没有这么好笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌，你真是笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.49,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如说是个连普通蜗牛都会当成\N法国蜗牛误食的大笨蛋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会搞错那种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实那家伙曾经在山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了奇怪的蘑菇笑了一整晚差点没挂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，不要那么暴力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到…内裤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，已经不要紧了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去躺一下休息吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，已经没什么大碍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道她是管理者的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何还收留她呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本只会招来麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是为了杀你的刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.38,0:16:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺客的话从以前就不少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她搞不好有什么目的才来接近你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样也没办法断定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你自己还有疑虑，那为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把那女孩子接到家里来照顾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌你其实也想要帮助那个女孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.52,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太白星在这场战争中扮演的是什么角色？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让地球人跟外星人的战争失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扮演着抑制他们的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天让双方互相了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手牵着手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起往同一个未来迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这个基础更加坚定的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意思是中立的角色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在两方都敌视我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是太可怜了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了不让希望的火苗熄灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非得有人做不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理者这组织有多恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.96,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌一直都没跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.20,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道把管理者的人留在家里会有多么危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.30,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但若对逃离组织的她见死不救的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类非坚持不可的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫370总觉得不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安藤美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样感觉好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安藤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当麻幌的妹妹会不会过头点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是太白星的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为疑神疑鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了怜悯心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就跟管理员没有两样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道我说这句话实在是太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想拜托史莱修跟流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有什么不测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.74,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们保护阿优吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还欠你人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会铭记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战士之间的约定我一定会遵守的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，装模作样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论你选择哪条路\N都会保护你和阿优的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少说什么丧气的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，我会害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优，美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚餐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.47,0:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！是！是！是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不请自来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多吃点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.19,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寿喜烧～寿喜烧～很好吃喔～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该放什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.63,0:20:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，阿优？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点吃就没得吃了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.27,0:21:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这块肉是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜也很好吃，要多吃点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和如果不多吃点肉\N会跟姐姐一样没有胸部哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
